flowchart TB
    N1["1. Neo N4 layer: Foreign-chain bridge program"]
    N2["2. Upstream domains: Solana instruction | token account state | bridge authority"]
    N3["3. neo-external-bridge-router: Solana-side bridge router that represents Neo N4 cross-chain lock, mint, burn, and unlock flows."]
    N4["4. Downstream domains: watcher-sol | gateway | shared bridge"]
    N5["5. Owned boundary: Validate route | Move escrowed assets | Emit bridge event"]
    N6["6. Outside boundary: does not own target-chain consensus; owns normalized relay semantics"]
    N7["7. Learning focus: Understand accepted facts, produced evidence, and next consumer."]
